		<br><br>
	<<elseif $_hordeLoot + $_matLoot + $_otherLoot gte 1>>
		You add them to the pile.
		<br><br>
	<<elseif $_hordeLoot + $_matLoot + $_otherLoot is 1>>
		You add it to the pile.
		<br><br>
	<</if>>

	<<if $_lurkerLoot gte 1>>
